{"id":"812061126385942528","type":"text","timestamp":1774441839,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/812061126385942528","is_reblog":false,"added_content":false,"tags":["gtg updates","Alexandria Updates","kitty posting","Zidormi posting","birbs and squirrels","transgender","lgbtq","mtf","lgbtqia","transbian","sapphic blog","sapphic","wlw","She's gotta catch them all!","Somehow!  🤔"],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p>So, my nesting partner brought home a new kitten a few weeks back and I may have made a mistake.</p><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"1113\" data-orig-width=\"546\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s640x960/7b0e9c9cb4116ec556ef6b20f5827fcd2fb4aca4.png\" data-orig-height=\"1113\" data-orig-width=\"546\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s75x75_c1/29c6abaa117371326d789af97fe99e4186051ad3.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s100x200/e17ba171e7cc5ded7cc7c93f146bfd02e25a9962.png 98w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s250x400/85eeeceb3cd6dceeee9bd20f53363a4296e22e31.png 196w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s400x600/110acd77d87fa9d157ea8ef9b4f2c290ad29de7e.png 294w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s500x750/ef4d6339e3abef567e6bba8f335097168f49209e.png 368w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s540x810/e37d6b3e4","reblog_comment":"<p>So, my nesting partner brought home a new kitten a few weeks back and I may have made a mistake.</p><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"1113\" data-orig-width=\"546\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s640x960/7b0e9c9cb4116ec556ef6b20f5827fcd2fb4aca4.png\" data-orig-height=\"1113\" data-orig-width=\"546\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s75x75_c1/29c6abaa117371326d789af97fe99e4186051ad3.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s100x200/e17ba171e7cc5ded7cc7c93f146bfd02e25a9962.png 98w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s250x400/85eeeceb3cd6dceeee9bd20f53363a4296e22e31.png 196w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s400x600/110acd77d87fa9d157ea8ef9b4f2c290ad29de7e.png 294w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s500x750/ef4d6339e3abef567e6bba8f335097168f49209e.png 368w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s540x810/e37d6b3e486471a8dd67d14fa8c874eb7aef5375.png 397w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s640x960/7b0e9c9cb4116ec556ef6b20f5827fcd2fb4aca4.png 471w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s1280x1920/73d8ebb2329e9f6304b219760571c94d828499fc.png 546w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 546px) 100vw, 546px\"></figure></div><p>(This is Zidormi, in this photo she was fascinated by the fact I’m shaving.)</p><p>I’m like, she is such a feisty little thing, I know she’ll love those youtube videos with birbs and squirrels and such.  And so I turn them on.  The first time I do, she was looking at my monitor from the side, so she kept looking at the screen and then looking behind the screen, trying to figure out where exactly those critters were.</p><p>Finally, she comes over to my lap and places her adorable little front paws on my desk…watching.  (With me only occasionally having to pull her back, since she’s ready to get closer and she’s not allowed on the desk.)  It was adorable and a grand old time.</p><p>Only now…now, she will randomly hop into my lap, put those paws up and be like, “MAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAHM!  I NEED THE BIRBS AND SQUIRRELS!” and it doesn’t matter what I’m doing…or even if there’s a keyboard on my lap….fnadshjlinfdgaskl.  In her little kitty brain, she needs to figure out how to get those critters and I need to make them show up, lol!</p>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"goodtransgirl"},"post":{"id":"812061126385942528"},"content_raw":"<p>So, my nesting partner brought home a new kitten a few weeks back and I may have made a mistake.</p><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"1113\" data-orig-width=\"546\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/a4d04da7316ff5ed2a4ebf222be8359c/a5d801e2406fcdc1-b2/s640x960/7b0e9c9cb4116ec556ef6b20f5827fcd2fb4aca4.png\" data-orig-height=\"1113\" data-orig-width=\"546\" srcset=\"htt"}],"baseline_notes":11,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}